This is a hopefully platform independent opencl compiler that spits out error messages and the like from your kernels.


Usage:
./compiler my_kernel.cl

Examples:

(good)
./compiler samples/test.cl
Found 1 platform(s)
NVIDIA CUDA
Found 1 devices
Created context
compiled samples/test.cl successfully

(bad)
./compiler samples/test.cl
Found 1 platform(s)
NVIDIA CUDA
Found 1 devices
Created context
Error Code: 0
:2: error: ilegal address space on image or sampler type
__constant sampler_t sampler = CLK_NORMALIZED_COORDS_FALSE | CLK_ADDRESS_CLAMP_TO_EDGE | CLK_FILTER_NEAREST;
^

